name: Steve Witters
text: I tried this place out yesterday and I gotta tell you... happily surprised.  They have a nicely diverse menu, I think they have something for everyone.  I ordered their version of Hawaiian pizza, it was the best I've had in quite a while. â€¦More

name: Tim Davis
text: Cozy atmosphere. Seating inside and outside. Very tasty menu. Pizza is good. Sides are good. Sandwiches are good.

name: villa villalobos
text: They had a great menu for both meat and veggie lovers. Descent selection of beer both bottles and draft. Pizza I ordered was good and was full after two slices. I would go back.

name: Bob Rubalcaba
text: We love this pizza. We miss the location in La Jolla. Please consider a location in South Orange County

name: Zig Ray
text: Only reason I gave one star is because I had to in order to give a review. Food was disgusting and will be giving it to the seagulls in the morning! Food was cold and the onion rings and curly fries were so limp and soggy they must have been straight from the freezer then heated up in microwave!

name: David Gladson
text: Extreme prices is more like it. Tasty, but not enough to justify the high prices.

name: Bridgett Tagoe
text: The only place that I know serves roasted potatoes on your pizza. Amazing!

name: Corinne Fischer
text: Great menu selection, Pizza tastes unique.

name: Bradford Bosley
text: Used to be good but prices have gone up and it was a bit greasy last time I went.
